110
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,880
Now you know the truth.

111
00:10:17,970 --> 00:10:19,370
Years ago, the Yin family

112
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,290
committed murder and arson

113
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,980
