our Lu family's pharmaceutical business.

114
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,430
I was lucky enough

115
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:29,080
to have escaped alive.

116
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,630
All I've done

117
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,270
is make the Yin family
pay for what they did

118
00:10:33,430 --> 00:10:35,750
and take back everything
that belongs to our Lu family.

119
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:36,840
But what about Yi?

120
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:39,670
What's the story with Yi?

121
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,750
Yi...

122
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,630
I failed Yi.

123
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,650
Back then, when I returned to the country,

124
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:49,600
I found Yi and told her the whole story.

125
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:52,600
She originally agreed to fight against
the Yin family with me,

126
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,730
and she could have used the engagement

127
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,430
to infiltrate the Yin family.

128
00:10:56,430 --> 00:10:57,910
