130
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:03,120
It was the Yin family
who's responsible for Yi's death.

131
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,320
Back then, Yin Zhuoyi

132
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,880
learned from her that I was still alive

133
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,540
and feared his dirty deeds
would be exposed,

134
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:11,000
so he ordered Yin Lei

135
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:12,720
to kill Yi.

136
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:17,220
That's not true.

137
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,900
That's not what Yin Zhuofeng told me.

138
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,550
My silly girl.

139
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,390
What you know

140
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:27,430
