141
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,320
He wouldn't lie to me.

142
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:31,960
Why wouldn't he?

143
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:33,480
Don't forget,

144
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,520
