149
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:43,430
Impossible!

150
00:11:45,410 --> 00:11:46,540
That's impossible.

151
00:11:48,340 --> 00:11:49,480
That's absolutely impossible.

152
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:51,550
If Yin Zhuofeng truly cared for you,

153
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,840
he wouldn't

154
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:53,750
have trained you to be

155
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,750
a sharp blade in his hands,

156
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:59,130
