163
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,030
It can't be.

164
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,420
He wouldn't lie to me.

165
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,770
How ridiculous.

166
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,580
I've hated One Heart

167
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,670
and the Priest so deeply

168
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,530
and been on this path for 15 years,

169
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,280
and now you're telling me

170
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,300
it all started because of Father?

171
00:12:38,810 --> 00:12:40,610
Father carried his own burdens.

172
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,400
The reason why Hai City

173
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:44,200
has managed to stay safe

174
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,360
amidst the chaos,

175
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:48,150
allowing the people
to live peaceful lives,

176
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:50,510
is entirely due to the prestige
of the Yin Army.

177
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:51,480
But in fact,

178
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:54,270
with military funds running low
year after year,

179
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:56,200
even the Yin Army
can't hold on much longer.

180
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,120
So you

181
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,270
