every day.

221
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:15,080
We never had a full meal.

222
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:17,810
All these years,

223
00:15:18,020 --> 00:15:20,050
it was Yi who kept the Lu family going

224
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,930
and held me up.

225
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:25,030
I've long forgotten that
I even had a father.

226
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:28,790
But I've

227
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:31,660
never forgotten about you and Yi.

228
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,490
Ye.

229
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,840
You and your sister

230
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,790
are the most precious people

231
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:45,030
