232
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:47,700
If it weren't for my concern for you,

233
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,550
this broken body of mine

234
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:52,060
would have been gone long ago.

235
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:54,720
I remember

236
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,160
how you always begged

237
00:15:57,750 --> 00:15:59,240
to ride on my shoulders

238
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:01,240
