239
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:04,360
Whenever I lifted you up high,

240
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:06,480
you'd laugh with such joy.

241
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:11,990
Who would've thought that now,

242
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,200
it's you who has to

243
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,840
hold up the Lu family,

244
00:16:18,510 --> 00:16:20,150
and me as well?

245
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,670
I'm not telling you this

246
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:38,030
to make you take my side,

247
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:39,630
nor to involve you

248
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:41,270
in any of my affairs,

249
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,200
but only to tell you

250
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,240
the truth.

251
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:56,000
Isn't there any other way

252
00:16:57,010 --> 00:17:00,210
to resolve the feud between our family
and the Yin family?

253
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:03,030
I'm already

254
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,079
a man who has died once.

255
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,599
The only reason

256
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,839
I've been hanging on to life

257
00:17:09,910 --> 00:17:12,040
is because of this one obsession.

258
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:14,990
As for you,

259
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,030
my daughter,

260
00:17:18,910 --> 00:17:20,319
I only want you

261
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:23,000
to live a peaceful life.

262
00:17:25,079 --> 00:17:26,319
That's the only way

263
00:17:26,829 --> 00:17:28,400
to honor your late mother

264
00:17:30,230 --> 00:17:31,390
and Yi.

265
00:17:43,390 --> 00:17:44,230
Father.

266
00:17:45,760 --> 00:17:47,090
You've suffered so much

267
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,870
in this lifetime.

268
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,310
But I've grown up now

269
00:18:00,100 --> 00:18:02,380
and am able to tell right from wrong.

270
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:13,000
I've said that family is my bottom line.

271
00:18:13,710 --> 00:18:15,080
In our deal,

272
00:18:15,470 --> 00:18:18,080
there was never any agreement
to harm family members.

273
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:18,950
Commander Yin.

274
00:18:19,390 --> 00:18:21,520
But your dear brother Yin Zhuofeng

275
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:25,080
did go on a killing spree
at Golden Pleasure.

276
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:27,470
