277
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:29,600
What about your daughter, Lu Ye?

278
00:18:30,230 --> 00:18:32,490
She was also once a member of Bronze Leaf.

279
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,620
In the Golden Pleasure incident,

280
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:36,530
she contributed significantly.

281
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,400
I understand.

282
00:18:37,990 --> 00:18:38,880
Commander Yin.

283
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:41,520
They are both family to us.

284
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,320
Of course I won't force you

285
00:18:43,340 --> 00:18:45,400
to kill your own brother, Commander.

286
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,670
But the existence of Bronze Leaf

287
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:50,280
is a major trouble for both of us.

288
00:18:50,410 --> 00:18:51,890
Taking back Bronze Leaf

289
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:54,360
won't be an easy task.

290
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,820
My second brother is a tough nut to crack.

291
00:18:57,080 --> 00:18:58,040
Perhaps

292
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,520
my daughter

293
00:18:59,710 --> 00:19:01,970
might just give you a pleasant surprise.

294
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,970
I'm here on behalf of my father,

295
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:22,670
specifically to help ease your burden,
Commander.
